The first batch of personal pension financial products are on sale, and the shortest can be held for only 360 days - CNN.com
First personal pension financial products go on sale
7 products from 7 institutions to choose from Minimum holding time of 360 days only
Personal pension financial products have finally gone live.
On February 10, China Wealth Management released the list of the first batch of personal pension financial products, and seven personal pension financial products from ICBC Wealth Management, Agricultural Bank of China Wealth Management and China Post Wealth Management were officially put on sale.
So far, the personal pension account "shelf" finally gathered personal pension savings, personal pension financial management, personal pension insurance, personal pension public fund four types of products.
According to reports, the first batch of personal pension financial products, all for the public placement class net-type open-ended products, including five new products, two surviving products, in addition to one product for mixed products, the remaining six products are fixed-income products.
The Beijing Youth Daily reporter saw that four of the five newly issued products were from ICBC Wealth Management, all of which were fixed-income products, with minimum holding periods of 365 days, 540 days, 720 days and 1080 days, and corresponding performance comparison benchmarks (annualized) of 3.70% - 4.20%, 4.10% - 4.60%, 4.40% - 4.90%, 5.25% - 5.75%. The benchmarks are 3.70% - 4.20%, 4.10% - 4.60%, 4.40% - 4.90%, 5.25% - 5.75%.
The remaining new product is "Postbank Wealth Tiyi-Hong Jin Minimum Holding Days 1,095 No. 1", which is also a fixed-income product, with the fund-raising process starting on February 10th and ending on February 19th, and with a risk rating of Level II.
Of the two surviving products, one is the "Agribank Concentric - Lingdang" 360-day technological innovation RMB financial product of Agribank Wealth Management, which is of mixed nature and has a risk level of Grade 3.
The other surviving product is "Postbank Wealth Tiyi-Hong Jin Minimum Holding 365 Days No. 1", fixed-income type, which was launched on December 30 last year and formally operated on January 4 this year, with a cumulative net value of 1.0011 on February 8, the product has been in the market for a long time and is expected to be launched in the near future.
According to the Opinions of the General Office of the State Council on Promoting the Development of Individual Pensions, the financial products in which funds in individual pension accounts can be invested include bank wealth management, savings deposits, commercial pension insurance and public funds.
The first batch of personal pension financial products are put on sale, marking the fact that personal pension investors can formally purchase financial products through their personal pension fund accounts.
In November last year, the CBIRC formulated the Interim Measures for the Administration of Personal Pension Businesses of Commercial Banks and Wealth Management Companies.
The Measures provide that participants may purchase personal pension products such as personal pension savings, personal pension financial products, personal pension insurance products and personal pension public fund products through their personal pension fund accounts.
Subsequently, the Ministry of Human Resources and Social Security, the Ministry of Finance and the State Administration of Taxation issued a notice specifying that the personal pension system was launched in Beijing and Tianjin, as well as 36 pioneer cities and regions such as Shijiazhuang and Xiong'an New Area in Hebei and Jincheng City in Shanxi.
By the end of 2022, there were 19.54 million individual pension participants, 6.13 million contributors, and total contributions of $14.2 billion.
Previously, the banks participating in the pilot program only had three types of products on their shelves: personal pension savings, personal pension insurance products and personal pension public funds.
Now, after the personal pension financial products are also gathered, how should investors choose?
Experts from the R&D department of CBI's financial products said that compared to other personal pension products, both the pilot stage pension financial products and personal pension financial products are characterized by three aspects.
The first is robustness, with a more robust risk management mechanism, more robust investment strategies and philosophies, and the implementation of independent third-party custodianship by a non-parent bank.
Second, long-term, the pilot phase of the pension financial products are five years and above, the next step in the issuance of personal pension financial products, the shortest holding period is in principle one year, encouraged to hold more than three years.
The third is universality, the product purchase threshold is low, the starting point is generally 1 yuan, some as low as 0.01 yuan, the product's custodian fee, management fee and other rates are more favorable.
Professionals pointed out that investors should choose according to the characteristics of the product and their own risk tolerance.
Personal pension savings have the characteristics of longer term, higher interest rate and high security, which are suitable for people with weak risk-tolerance ability; personal pension insurance products emphasize on protection, which are more suitable for people who can't bear the investment risk and can accept the stable income; and personal pension financial products and public fund products don't guarantee the capital or the income, which have a certain investment risk, but the expected income is higher, which is suitable for people who have a certain degree of financial knowledge and higher risk-tolerance ability. They have certain investment risks but higher expected returns, and are suitable for people with certain financial knowledge and higher risk-bearing ability.
